{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/82344", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/82344/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/82344/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/82344/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/82344", "id": 812698647, "node_id": "MDU6SXNzdWU4MTI2OTg2NDc=", "number": 82344, "title": "Standard streams hold a lock while executing arbitrary user code", "user": {"login": "tmiasko", "id": 51362316, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjUxMzYyMzE2", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/51362316?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/tmiasko", "html_url": "https://github.com/tmiasko", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tmiasko/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tmiasko/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tmiasko/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tmiasko/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tmiasko/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tmiasko/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tmiasko/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tmiasko/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tmiasko/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [{"id": 650731663, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWw2NTA3MzE2NjM=", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/labels/C-bug", "name": "C-bug", "color": "f5f1fd", "default": false, "description": "Category: This is a bug."}, {"id": 2011781731, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWwyMDExNzgxNzMx", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/labels/T-libs", "name": "T-libs", "color": "bfd4f2", "default": false, "description": "Relevant to the library team, which will review and decide on the PR/issue."}], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 4, "created_at": "2021-02-20T20:17:22Z", "updated_at": "2021-05-23T17:12:43Z", "closed_at": "2021-05-23T17:12:43Z", "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "The implementation of `Write::write_fmt` for `&Stdout` & `&Stderr` holds an\r\ninternal lock while executing an arbitrary user code. As a result, it might\r\nintroduce a lock order inversion and a deadlock, either between themselves or\r\nanother user held lock. For example:\r\n\r\n```rust\r\nuse std::fmt::*;\r\n\r\n#[derive(Copy, Clone)]\r\nenum Print { Out, Err }\r\n\r\nimpl Display for Print {\r\n    fn fmt(&self, _f: &mut Formatter) -> Result {\r\n        match self {\r\n            Print::Out => print!(\"\"),\r\n            Print::Err => eprint!(\"\"),\r\n        }\r\n        Ok(())\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\nfn run() {\r\n    for _ in 0..1000 {\r\n        print!(\"{}\", Print::Err);\r\n        eprint!(\"{}\", Print::Out);\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\nfn main() {\r\n    let t = std::thread::spawn(run);\r\n    run();\r\n    t.join().unwrap();\r\n}\r\n```\r\n", "closed_by": {"login": "tmiasko", "id": 51362316, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjUxMzYyMzE2", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/51362316?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/tmiasko", "html_url": "https://github.com/tmiasko", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tmiasko/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tmiasko/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tmiasko/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tmiasko/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tmiasko/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tmiasko/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tmiasko/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/u